ibre/MLNEmptyFeature":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNEmptyFeature","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNEmptyFeature","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnemptyfeature","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNEmptyFeature"},{"type":"text","text":" object associates an empty shape with an optional"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"identifier and attributes."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNEmptyFeature"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNLineStyleLayer":{"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNLineStyleLayer","type":"reference"},{"text":" is a style layer that renders one or more stroked","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"polylines on the map.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNLineStyleLayer","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNLineStyleLayer"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnlinestylelayer","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNLineStyleLayer","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolylineFeature":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolylineFeature","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolylineFeature"},{"type":"text","text":" object associates a multipolyline shape with an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"optional identifier and attributes."}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNMultiPolylineFeature","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolylinefeature","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolylineFeature","role":"symbol"},"doc://or